<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
Pricilla_Asagiri wrote:<BR>
<DIV>If they come as we fear we have little choise ,but ask yourself:</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Do you want one sided changes now so that in 2 to 4 expansions your at the same point that you are now? Is it nessesarry to tip the scale in favor of one or another class each expasion only to change the overall balace either in vafor of another in the next or worse fixing it by contends wich in turn make earlyer fixes obsolete. Thats the reson i highly would like to see that they consider what impact the change of one class has on the whole picture and do ajustment at the same time instead of just looking at a narow picture.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Well its only the opening but the overall message showed that cusomer service really botched before releasing this one <img src='/i/smilies/16x16_smiley-wink.gif' width=16 height=16 border=0></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Well we will see </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Pricilla Asagiri 70 Dark Elf Cleric of Innoruuk</DIV><BR>
